  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/9651e214bae32761d75e46f4c5bf3121.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHAKHTER-ONE</h2>Horrors wake up once again on board Shakhter-One. The history of Mark's mental tragedy and family life comes clearer with every minute spent on this hollowed spaceship. The curse of a never-ending loop can only be stopped by one thing – the truth. But all the secrets are kept jealously by these dark corridors blended with Mark's memories.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREAK THE CYCLE</h2>In Hollow 2, exploring and surviving won't be enough to learn your past and unravel all secrets. With re-designed, fast, and friendly mechanics, your mission is to purge an abandoned station in order to reach your goal. Use all weapons and tools you find to make sure that not even a single creature can stand between you and the truth. Run, fight, hide, explore – do your best to destroy the Shakhter-One once and forever!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/9651e214bae32761d75e46f4c5bf3121.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/2be94aa0e7019abd264315df5196ae9c.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHAKHTER-ONE</h2>Horrors wake up once again on board Shakhter-One. The history of Mark's mental tragedy and family life comes clearer with every minute spent on this hollowed spaceship. The curse of a never-ending loop can only be stopped by one thing – the truth. But all the secrets are kept jealously by these dark corridors blended with Mark's memories.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/06176dcf24a8ddb2fb1761623197b28c.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREAK THE CYCLE</h2>In Hollow 2, exploring and surviving won't be enough to learn your past and unravel all secrets. With re-designed, fast, and friendly mechanics, your mission is to purge an abandoned station in order to reach your goal. Use all weapons and tools you find to make sure that not even a single creature can stand between you and the truth. Run, fight, hide, explore – do your best to destroy the Shakhter-One once and forever!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.poster.avif?t=1657274503\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.webm?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055240/extras/96b7b27aa8c1380c5e030e853a4cc28a.mp4?t=1657274503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
